      "content": "those are good, thanks. i'm worried though, some of my regular customers are pretty old school and might see the word 'equity' or 'DEI' and think we're getting too political. maybe u can give me some more options that are a bit more subtle? like, how can I show we're inclusive without it sounding like a social justice statement or something?",
